description: The French president's popularity has fallen during the crisis - now he faces delayed local elections.
title: France's Macron set for Covid test in local vote
title_page: France's Macron set for Covid test in local vote - BBC News
maintext: "We had a lot of cases in the east of France, then the virus travelled to Paris, and next it would have been Normandy," he said. "So for us, here in Le Havre, the lockdown arrived bang on time. There weren't too many cases, too many victims, and our hospitals weren't swamped like in other regions."
